Sherie Rene Scott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sherie_Rene_Scott 0 Sherie Rene Scott (born February 8, 1967) is an American actress, singer, writer and producer. She has been seen in multiple Broadway and Off-Broadway plays/musicals, on numerous solo and original cast recordings, and in various television roles in episodic and feature film.
